# watib CLI surface (decoded from args-parse spec
# at watib.scm:42-128):
#   --help / -h                 display help and quit
#   --keep-going / -k           continue on error
#   --stop-after N              stop after N errors
#   -s                          silent (less verbose errors)
#   -j N                        use N threads
#   --validate-only / -v        validate only
#   -O0                         disable all optimisations
#   -O1                         enable all optimisations (default)
#   -fno-testbr / -ftestbr      type-based control-flow rewriting
#   -fno-copyprop / -fcopyprop  copy propagation
#   -fno-uncast / -funcast      redundant cast/test elimination
#   -fno-unreachable / -funreachable  unreachable-code elimination
#   -fno-const / -fconst        constant folding
#   -fno-puredrop / -fpuredrop  redundant drop elimination
#   -fno-peephole / -fpeephole  peephole optimisation
#   -o FILE                     output binary path (default: a.out.wasm)
#   --dump-cfg FUNC             dump CFG of FUNC in graphviz DOT
#   --dump-cfg-wat FUNC         dump CFG of FUNC in CFGWAT format
#   --read-cfg FILE             read CFG from FILE and dump it
#
# Positional: input WAT files (one or more)
