# Bigloo Scheme.  Validates WAT (WebAssembly Text)
# files, applies type-based and dataflow-based
# optimizations, emits WASM binary.  Authored by
# Aghilas Y. Boussaa (4y8).  2 GH stars (recent
# project).  Sister tools: wabt (WebAssembly
# Binary Toolkit, in corpus as `_wabt`), wasm-
# tools (Rust wasm tooling, in corpus),
# wasm-pack (in corpus), wasmtime (in corpus).
