# Critical extraction note: watib uses **Bigloo
# `args-parse` macro with case-clause-with-
# embedded-body CLI pattern** at watib.scm:42-129
# — `(args-parse args ((CLAUSE) BODY) ... (else
# BODY))`.  Each clause is a 2-element list:
# `(PATTERN-MATCH BODY-EXPR)`.  The pattern can be
