# SPEC)` (function call with quoted-alist spec,
# returns alist — NO embedded body), R324
# Chicken `args:make-option` (similar embedded
# body but uses egg-based spec).  Bigloo's
# approach: MACRO-EXPANDED CASE-CLAUSE MATCHING
# with EMBEDDED BODY per case — corpus's **first
# documented case-clause-args-parse-with-
# embedded-body CLI pattern**.
