# BODY) (("-ftestbr" ...) BODY) (("-O0" ...) BODY)
# (("-O1" ...) BODY)`.  Bigloo's args-parse
# handles ALPHANUMERIC SUFFIXED short flags via
# STRING MATCHING (not single-char dispatch).
# Distinct from R325 OCaml `Arg.Set` single-char
# convention, R322 JCommander reflection-based,
# R272 C POSIX getopt's option-string (single
